def: A first-formed organized body; the first individual, or pair ofindividuals, of a species.A species is a class of individuals, each of which is hypotheticallyconsidered to be the descendant of the same protoplast, or of thesame pair of protoplasts. Latham.
An artificial water trench, esp. one to or from a mill. C.Kingsley.
an East Indian name for several twining leguminous plantsrelated to the bean, but commonly applied to the hyacinth bean(Delichos Lablab).
A bullying and violent person; a braggart; a swashbuckler.[Obs.]That flock of stout, bragging rushbucklers. Robynson (More's Utopia).
Of or pertaining to, or characterized by, exophthalmia.Exophthalmic golter. Same as Rasedow's disease.
In a faded manner.A dull room fadedly furnished. Dickens.
An aromatic preparation of carbonate of ammonia and, often,some scent, to avoid or relieve faintness, headache, or the like.
A Hindoo measure of distance, varying from one and a half totwo English miles. Whitworth.
Stolen; obtained or characterized by stealth; sly; secret;stealthy; as, a furtive look. Prior.A hasty and furtive ceremony. Hallam.
